The cheers and ululations heard as the clips were viewed and spread clearly replicated the reactions of those who watched ‘live’ the great performances Ms Jumwa and Mr Sifuna at separate campaign events for the Msambweni Parliamentary by-election.
Ms Jumwa, a renegade ODM MP, is part of the brigade campaigning for Independent candidate Feisal Bader, who enjoys the patronage of Deputy President William Ruto. Mr Sifuna, on the other hand, was stumping for the ODM flagbearer Omar Boga, who is being backed not just by the party leader Raila Odinga, but also by President Uhuru Kenyatta.



