The language employed in that toxic exchange cannot be reproduced in a decent newspaper. Ms Jumwa is an Honourable Member of Parliament. Mr Sifuna is an aspiring Honourable after putting in a decent performance in the race for Nairobi Senator at the 2017 General Election.
Political animal
From the respective ends of the political spectrum, they are an insult to the honorific. However, they are only acting in the best tradition of the Kenyan political animal, in which regard their platform histrionics can be considered stellar.
You could see from the video clips that their respective crowds were appreciative of the charged vulgarity. They cheered and egged them on and no doubt welcomed them back to their seats with hearty high-fives and fist bumps.



